00:34:20.780 --> 00:34:25.190
the Asia countries and their ascendancy versus
America in

00:34:25.190 --> 00:34:26.190
the near future.

00:34:26.190 --> 00:34:28.409
&gt;&gt; Gary: Yeah, I don't think there's a great
