00:42:08.500 --> 00:42:11.010
&gt;&gt; Female Presenter: Is it a mini series.

00:42:11.010 --> 00:42:15.090
&gt;&gt; Gary: Not like a fiction series because
what's happened is

00:42:15.090 --> 00:42:18.320
so much of fiction has really moved to the
screen -- to

00:42:18.320 --> 00:42:21.410
the small screen, not the big screen -- a
lot of

00:42:21.410 --> 00:42:23.810
writers -- well, you look at shows like the
Sopranos and

00:42:23.810 --> 00:42:28.990
the Wire. The Wire is written by writers like
Richard Price,

00:42:28.990 --> 00:42:33.290
excellent novelist. And things like the Sopranos
and the

00:42:33.290 --> 00:42:37.000
