00:42:48.860 --> 00:42:50.900
hard. You have a white-collar job. You come
home. The last thing you

00:42:50.900 --> 00:42:54.100
want to do is read 400-page text. But things
like the

00:42:54.100 --> 00:42:56.590
Wire and Soprano allow you to enjoy the narrative
energy

00:42:56.590 --> 00:43:01.360
narrative momentum on the screen without having
to read.

00:43:01.360 --> 00:43:03.500
