different

00:43:36.580 --> 00:43:40.560
ways are – it's, you used to be able -- you
write a decent

00:43:40.560 --> 00:43:42.620
book, you get good reviews and people would
buy hundreds

00:43:42.620 --> 00:43:44.930
of thousands of copies. Now to sell those
hundreds of

00:43:44.930 --> 00:43:47.780
thousands of copies you have to create -- you
