00:44:00.300 --> 00:44:04.350
more people would show up. Which is nice.
You have to

00:44:04.350 --> 00:44:07.230
do -- you have to promote the book face to
face

00:44:07.230 --> 00:44:09.970
everywhere you can. Because a lot of the NPR
outlets no

00:44:09.970 --> 00:44:13.550
longer do -- have the authors. You'll still
can get on

00:44:13.550 --> 00:44:16.040
