00:44:24.060 --> 00:44:28.190
I'm fine with having 3,000
readers. And they're great readers and I don't

00:44:28.190 --> 00:44:31.250
want
anymore. But being, you know, small, furry,

00:44:31.250 --> 00:44:33.290
hungry
immigrant that's not going to do it for me.

00:44:33.290 --> 00:44:38.190
I want the
Times best seller list. So I put in a lot

00:44:38.190 --> 00:44:41.120
of work. It
takes about a year or more. Year and a half

00:44:41.120 --> 00:44:43.490
to promote a
book. A year to promote in the states, another

00:44:43.490 --> 00:44:48.890
