00:44:48.890 --> 00:44:51.280
that year and a half, I could have written
another book in

00:44:51.280 --> 00:44:53.990
the meantime. So the dynamics for the writer
has

00:44:53.990 --> 00:44:57.840
changed. Now will there be another resurgence
of literature all of a sudden that's somehow

00:44:57.840 --> 00:45:01.570
s
based on these platforms? Wow that would be

