00:48:23.520 --> 00:48:28.110
almost like
relegated to the extinct vocabulary, because

00:48:28.110 --> 00:48:33.181
you know now
it's like, “JBF, it's freezing”. And part

00:48:33.181 --> 00:48:37.220
of freezing would
probably be like 4 easing. [laughter]On the

00:48:37.220 --> 00:48:41.300
