out. I

00:48:57.930 --> 00:49:00.280
don't know if the Spanish Academy does the
same. But

00:49:00.280 --> 00:49:03.140
there is one. It's constantly worried about
the purity

00:49:03.140 --> 00:49:07.940
of the language, which is a very European
concept trying to protect the purity of th

00:49:07.940 --> 00:49:11.140
language whereas
